### ========================================
### CRUD TESTING FOR USERS
### ========================================

### 1. CREATE a new User (POST)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "nationalId": "1199080000000000",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "CITIZEN"
}

###

### 2. READ all Users (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. READ a single User by ID (GET)
### (Assuming the created user got ID 1)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. DELETE a User (DELETE)
### (Assuming the created user got ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/users/1

###


### ========================================
### CRUD TESTING FOR DOCUMENTS
### ========================================

### 1. CREATE a new Document (POST)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "ID Card",
  "filePath": "/uploads/id-card.pdf",
  "applicationId": 1
}

###

### 2. READ all Documents (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/documents
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. READ a single Document by ID (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/documents/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. DELETE a Document (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/documents/1
